column5: I never knew much about PACE etc, but when I was finally diagnosed last year after 10 years of knowing what I had and being written off, my Dr suggested a clinic to help. When I researched it, i saw it was PACE and the more I read I just had a bad feeling and didn't pursue it! Glad I did now after hearing so much more about it!!
